queries.sql: SELECT `tb1`.`id`, `tb1`.`keyword`, `tb2`.`title`, `tb1`.`userid_created`, `tb1`.`userid_updated`, `tb1`.`created_at`, `tb1`.`updated_at` FROM `slide_catalogue` as `tb1` INNER JOIN `slide_translate` as `tb2` ON `tb1`.`id` = `tb2`.`objectid` AND `tb2`.`module` = "slide_catalogue" AND `tb2`.`language` = 'vi' WHERE `tb1`.`deleted_at` = 0 GROUP BY `tb1`.`id` ORDER BY `tb1`.`id` desc LIMIT 20
